[30;1m21 | [0m[35mcmd2 is a tool for building interactive command line applications in Python. Its goal is to make it[0m
[30;1m22 | [0m[35mquick and easy for developers to build feature-rich and user-friendly interactive command line[0m
[30;1m23 | [0m[35mapplications. It provides a simple API which is an extension of Python's built-in[0m
[30;1m24 | [0m[35m[cmd](https://docs.python.org/3/library/cmd.html) module. cmd2 provides a wealth of features on top[0m
[30;1m25 | [0m[35mof cmd to make your life easier and eliminates much of the boilerplate code which would be necessary[0m
[30;1m26 | [0m[35mwhen using cmd.[0m

[30;1m71 | [0m[35mcmd2 is a tool for building interactive command line applications in Python. Its goal is to make it[0m
[30;1m72 | [0m[35mquick and easy for developers to build feature-rich and user-friendly interactive command line[0m
[30;1m73 | [0m[35mapplications. It provides a simple API which is an extension of Python's built-in[0m
[30;1m74 | [0m[35m[cmd](https://docs.python.org/3/library/cmd.html) module. cmd2 provides a wealth of features on top[0m

[30;1m29 | [0m[35m[0m
